#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A leader in environmental protection. <br/>Committed, knowledgeable, and "
"always striving for sustainability. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຜູ້ນຳໃນການປົກປ້ອງສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ. <br/>ມີຄວາມມຸ່ງໝັ້ນ, ມີຄວາມຮູ້, ແລະ "
"ພະຍາຍາມເພື່ອຄວາມຍືນຍົງສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Outstanding efforts and results! <br/>They consistently advance our "
"mission to protect the planet. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຄວາມພະຍາຍາມ ແລະ ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ! <br/"
">ພວກເຂົາສືບຕໍ່ຜັກດັນພາລະກິດຂອງພວກເຮົາໃນການປົກປ້ອງໂລກຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ. \""

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their impact on conservation is profound. <br/>Innovative, effective, and "
"dedicated to the environment. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຜົນກະທົບຂອງພວກເຂົາຕໍ່ການອະນຸລັກແມ່ນມີຄວາມໝາຍເລິກເຊິ່ງ. <br/>ມີນະວັດຕະກຳ, ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ແລະ "
"ອຸທິດຕົນເພື່ອສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ. \""

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_image
msgid "<b>ABOUT US</b>"
msgstr "<b>ກ່ຽວກັບພວກເຮົາ</b>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Environmental protection is the practice of safeguarding the natural "
"world from harmful human activities and preserving ecosystems for future "
"generations. It involves efforts to reduce pollution, conserve biodiversity, "
"and sustainably manage natural resources such as air, water, and soil.\n"
"        <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ການປົກປ້ອງສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມແມ່ນການປະຕິບັດເພື່ອປົກປັກຮັກສາໂລກທຳມະຊາດຈາກກິດຈະກຳຂອງມະນຸດທີ່ເປັນອັນຕະລາຍ "
"ແລະ ຮັກສາລະບົບນິເວດໄວ້ໃຫ້ຄົນລຸ້ນຫຼັງ. ມັນລວມເຖິງຄວາມພະຍາຍາມໃນການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນມົນລະພິດ, "
"ອະນຸລັກຄວາມຫຼາກຫຼາຍທາງຊີວະນາໆພັນ, ແລະ ຄຸ້ມຄອງຊັບພະຍາກອນທຳມະຊາດຢ່າງຍືນຍົງ ເຊັ່ນ: ອາກາດ, ນ້ຳ, "
"ແລະ ດິນ.\n"
"        <br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_sidegrid
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Every step we take towards sustainability is a commitment to "
"preserving nature's beauty and resources, for today and tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ທຸກໆບາດກ້າວທີ່ພວກເຮົາກ້າວໄປສູ່ຄວາມຍືນຍົງ ແມ່ນຄວາມມຸ່ງໝັ້ນທີ່ຈະຮັກສາຄວາມສວຍງາມ ແລະ "
"ຊັບພະຍາກອນຂອງທຳມະຊາດ ໄວ້ສຳລັບມື້ນີ້ ແລະ ມື້ອື່ນ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        From carbon footprint reduction to renewable energy adoption and "
"biodiversity preservation, our key milestones reflect our commitment to "
"creating a sustainable future for all."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ນັບແຕ່ການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການປ່ອຍອາຍກາກບອນ ຈົນເຖິງການນຳໃຊ້ພະລັງງານທົດແທນ ແລະ "
"ການອະນຸລັກຄວາມຫຼາກຫຼາຍທາງຊີວະນາໆພັນ, "
"ຜົນສຳເລັດອັນສຳຄັນຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ສະທ້ອນເຖິງຄວາມມຸ່ງໝັ້ນໃນການສ້າງອະນາຄົດທີ່ຍືນຍົງສຳລັບທຸກຄົນ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_cover
msgid ""
"<br/>Highlight your environmental initiatives and projects with a user-"
"friendly platform that simplifies all the steps, from setup to campaign "
"management, making it easy to engage supporters and drive positive change."
"<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ເນັ້ນໜັກແຜນງານ ແລະ ໂຄງການດ້ານສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍແພລດຟອມທີ່ນຳໃຊ້ງ່າຍ "
"ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທຸກຂັ້ນຕອນງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈົນເຖິງການຈັດການແຄມເປນ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ການດຶງດູດຜູ້ສະໜັບສະໜູນ "
"ແລະ ການສ້າງການປ່ຽນແປງໃນທາງບວກກາຍເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ.<br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Immerse yourself in peaceful environments that harmonize with nature."
"<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ດື່ມດ່ຳກັບສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ງຽບສະຫງົບ ເຊິ່ງປະສົມປະສານເຂົ້າກັບທຳມະຊາດຢ່າງລົງຕົວ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_split_intro
msgid ""
"<br/>Join us in making a positive impact on the environment. We offer "
"solutions and initiatives that promote sustainability and conservation, from "
"reducing waste to supporting green practices. Together, we can create a "
"healthier planet and ensure a thriving future for generations to come.<br/"
"><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ຮ່ວມກັບພວກເຮົາໃນການສ້າງຜົນກະທົບທາງບວກຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ. ພວກເຮົາສະເໜີວິທີການ ແລະ "
"ແຜນງານທີ່ສົ່ງເສີມຄວາມຍືນຍົງ ແລະ ການອະນຸລັກ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອ "
"ຈົນເຖິງການສະໜັບສະໜູນການປະຕິບັດທີ່ເປັນມິດຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ. ພວກເຮົາສາມາດຮ່ວມກັນສ້າງໂລກທີ່ດີຂຶ້ນ ແລະ "
"ຮັບປະກັນອະນາຄົດທີ່ສົດໃສໃຫ້ແກ່ຄົນລຸ້ນຫຼັງ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cover
msgid "<font style=\"font-size: 62px;\">— Life on Earth —</font>"
msgstr "<font style=\"font-size: 62px;\">— ຊີວິດເທິງໂລກ —</font>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Eco-"
"friendly retreats"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/"
">  ສະຖານທີ່ພັກຜ່ອນທີ່ເປັນມິດຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">1.2 Billion</span><br/>\n"
"        Liters of water saved"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">1.2 ຕື້</span><br/>\n"
"        ລິດຂອງນ້ຳທີ່ປະຢັດໄດ້"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">2 Million</span><br/>\n"
"        Trees Planted"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">2 ລ້ານ</span><br/>\n"
"        ຕົ້ນໄມ້ທີ່ປູກແລ້ວ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">45%</span><br/>\n"
"        Reduction in carbon emissions"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">45%</span><br/>\n"
"        ການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການປ່ອຍອາຍກາກບອນ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">500,000</span><br/>\n"
"        Tons of materials recycled"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">500,000</span><br/>\n"
"        ໂຕນຂອງວັດສະດຸທີ່ນຳມາໃຊ້ໃໝ່"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">60%</span><br/>\n"
"        Renewable Energy usage"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">60%</span><br/>\n"
"        ການນຳໃຊ້ພະລັງງານທົດແທນ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">85%</span><br/>\n"
"        Waste diversion rate"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">85%</span><br/>\n"
"        ອັດຕາການຄັດແຍກຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "A Call for Environmental Protection"
msgstr "ສຽງຮຽກຮ້ອງເພື່ອການປົກປ້ອງສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_image_title
msgid "A Deep Dive into Conservation and Impact"
msgstr "ເຈາະເລິກເລື່ອງການອະນຸລັກ ແລະ ຜົນກະທົບ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_key_benefits
msgid ""
"Access specialized knowledge and innovative practices that enhance your "
"understanding and effectiveness in environmental stewardship."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າເຖິງຄວາມຮູ້ສະເພາະດ້ານ ແລະ ແນວທາງປະຕິບັດທີ່ມີນະວັດຕະກຳ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄວາມເຂົ້າໃຈ ແລະ "
"ປະສິດທິພາບໃນການເບິ່ງແຍງສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_freegrid
msgid "Be Part of the Change"
msgstr "ຮ່ວມເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງການປ່ຽນແປງ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_card_offset
msgid "Be part of the change."
msgstr "ຮ່ວມເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid "Book a stay"
msgstr "ຈອງບ່ອນພັກ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Certification services for buildings aiming to meet green standards, "
"including energy efficiency assessments and sustainable materials consulting."
msgstr ""
"ບໍລິການອອກໃບຢັ້ງຢືນສຳລັບອາຄານທີ່ຕັ້ງເປົ້າໝາຍໃຫ້ໄດ້ມາດຕະຖານສີຂຽວ, "
"ລວມທັງການປະເມີນປະສິດທິພາບພະລັງງານ ແລະ ການໃຫ້ຄຳປຶກສາດ້ານວັດສະດຸທີ່ຍືນຍົງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_title
msgid "Changing the world is possible.<br/> We’ve done it before."
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນແປງໂລກແມ່ນເປັນໄປໄດ້.<br/> ພວກເຮົາເຄີຍເຮັດມາແລ້ວ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_unveil
msgid "Collaborate for a thriving planet and a sustainable future."
msgstr "ຮ່ວມມືກັນເພື່ອໂລກທີ່ສົດໃສ ແລະ ອະນາຄົດທີ່ຍືນຍົງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cards_grid
msgid "Committed to a Greener Future"
msgstr "ມຸ່ງໝັ້ນເພື່ອອະນາຄົດທີ່ຂຽວງາມກວ່າ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cards_grid
msgid "Community Engagement"
msgstr "ການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຂອງຊຸມຊົນ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_key_images
msgid "Community-driven projects for a greener future"
msgstr "ໂຄງການທີ່ຂັບເຄື່ອນໂດຍຊຸມຊົນເພື່ອອະນາຄົດທີ່ຂຽວງາມກວ່າ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Comprehensive restoration of natural habitats to support wildlife "
"conservation, including reforestation and wetland revitalization."
msgstr ""
"ການຟື້ນຟູບ່ອນຢູ່ອາໄສຕາມທຳມະຊາດຢ່າງຮອບດ້ານເພື່ອສະໜັບສະໜູນການອະນຸລັກສັດປ່າ, ລວມທັງການປູກປ່າຄືນໃໝ່ "
"ແລະ ການຟື້ນຟູເຂດດິນຊຸ່ມ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_carousel_intro
msgid ""
"Contribute to a healthier planet with our initiatives that promote "
"sustainability, preserve ecosystems, and combat climate change."
msgstr ""
